  "title": "Senior Office Admin",
  "description": "<p>Admin role job scope :</p><p>-\tAssist with sales and support team with all related admin works</p><p>-\tTender preparation and other paperwork</p><p>-\tReceiving goods and pass to accountant to enter to accounting system</p><p>-\tAssist in scheduling meetings, call, and coordinating travel arrangements for sales team </p><p>-\tManaging promotional materials and events preparation</p><p>-\tAssisting accountant with the preparation of sales contracts, price quotations and ensuring invoices are issued correctly</p><p>-\tCoordinating logistics: liaising with warehouse, dispatch, and shipping teams to ensure timely and accurate delivery of the products and sample requests, prepare instrument sets and implant boxes for internal coordination for daily cases.</p><p>-\tSupport the sales reps: being the main internal contact for the sales team. Answering questions, providing orders status updates, and escalating technical queries. </p><p>-\tCustomer services: handling inbound customer inquires about orders, stock availability or basic product information, ensuring a smooth after-sales experiences</p><p>-\tMaintaining Sales records: keep sales record data excel updated daily order history</p><p>-\tKeep paperwork/contracts hard copy in folder</p>",
